HEADWORD: Entrail
<hw>En*trail"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>en-</ets> + OF. <ets>treiller</ets> to grate, lattice, F.
<ets>treille</ets> vine, arbor. See <er>Trellis</er>.]</ety> <def>To
interweave; to intertwine.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

